    // ── Creator hosting applications ─────────────────────────────────────────
    // Creators can request review for hosted challenge readiness. Admins can
    // use reviewCreatorHostingApplication to update reviewNote, reviewedBy,
    // reviewedAt, and status. This is a manual admin queue only: no contracts,
